WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:03.263
Carroll was convicted in 2004

00:03.380 --> 00:05.554
for the murders
of 14 young women.

00:05.653 --> 00:08.209
The warden granted Joe
Carroll's request for a transfer.

00:08.303 --> 00:08.985
He's leaving.

00:09.071 --> 00:10.509
Joe's not in the
transport vehicle.

00:10.604 --> 00:11.580
Where the hell is he?

00:13.333 --> 00:15.521
So Joe's free,
and now I get locked up.

00:15.618 --> 00:17.421
Protective custody.
Better if I don't know.

00:17.525 --> 00:20.292
Hey. Morning. I know
you're scared of me,

00:20.393 --> 00:21.771
but I hope that will change.

00:21.871 --> 00:24.347
My son needs a mother.

00:24.438 --> 00:25.850
And I have an idea
how we can find her.

00:25.956 --> 00:27.448
She has to die

00:27.554 --> 00:29.534
because you slept
with Joe's wife.

00:29.619 --> 00:31.078
Why did you do it?

00:31.252 --> 00:32.461
Because I love her.

00:32.566 --> 00:34.713
Nick Donovan made an
encrypted cell phone call

00:34.821 --> 00:36.492
checking the status
of Claire Matthews.

00:36.591 --> 00:38.410
Your wife is
in Huntington County.

00:39.516 --> 00:40.958
What's taking her so long?

00:41.081 --> 00:41.945
I looked all over the place!

00:42.048 --> 00:43.030
She and Joey are both gone!

00:43.191 --> 00:44.453
Aah!

00:44.733 --> 00:46.461
Emma, why did you leave us?

00:46.549 --> 00:48.346
If you don't get
him to a hospital immediately,

00:48.431 --> 00:49.279
he's going to die.

00:49.376 --> 00:50.490
You can do this.

00:51.591 --> 00:52.866
I'm sorry.

00:52.940 --> 00:54.700
Earlier I received
a very exciting e-mail.

00:54.808 --> 00:55.971
I wanted to tell you about it,

00:56.067 --> 00:57.569
but I thought I'd surprise you.

